================================================================================
GPL-Licensed Tools (Distributed Separately)
================================================================================

The following tools are GPL-licensed and are NOT included in the main
HuskyCat distribution. They are available as a separate optional container:

- shellcheck: Shell script static analysis tool
  Copyright (c) Vidar Holen
  License: GPL-3.0

- hadolint: Dockerfile linter
  Copyright (c) hadolint contributors
  License: GPL-3.0

- yamllint: YAML linter
  Copyright (c) Adrien Verge
  License: GPL-3.0

These tools are isolated via IPC and run in a separate process/container
to maintain license compliance. See gpl-sidecar/ for details.

================================================================================
Clean-Room Implementations
================================================================================

The following components were implemented using clean-room techniques based
on public specifications, without reference to GPL-licensed implementations:

- src/huskycat/linters/yaml_lint.py
  Based on: YAML 1.2 Specification (https://yaml.org/spec/1.2/)
  License: Apache-2.0 (original implementation)

